{"tid":405990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"控制桿太難用，美軍核動力潛艇改用Xbox 360控制器？","createTime":"2017-09-19T09:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T14:09:48.000Z","uid":53379,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2388db9501ebd334d0d3feaa6d039c6d63eef273","tid":405990,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控制桿太難用，美軍核動力潛艇改用Xbox 360控制器？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2017/9/l44xa3jgu24gbl92emvw0zdf59va7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F9%2Fl44xa3jgu24gbl92emvw0zdf59va7u.jpg&h=41595b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國海軍的維珍尼亞級（Virginia-class）核動力潛艇以裝可以作高清攝錄的光電船桅（photonics mast）取代傳統的潛望鏡，拍下來的畫面會顯示在控制室內的大屏幕，並以控制桿來操控。<br />\n<br />\n當美軍向軍官及水手詢問如何可以改善潛艇時，其中一個重要問題是難以控制鏡頭，因為控制桿太笨重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是美國海軍及Lockheed Martin開始着手解決問題，他們把目標鎖定在已推出市埸的技術，一來可以降低成本，二來水手亦會較為熟悉，結果他們找到控制桿的替代品︰Xbox 360控制器&mdash;&mdash;並計劃將這款控制器整合到潛艇控制室。<br />\n<br />\nLockheed Martin表示，在他們的實驗室測試中，參與的水手自行在幾分鐘內就弄清楚如何使用控制器，時間明顯比控制桿所需的數小時訓練短。<br />\n<br />\n此外，採用Xbox控制器要便宜得多，原本的控制面板成本約3萬8千美元，但能以不夠30美元的Xbox控制器代替，要替換亦更為方便。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍表示，系統已在過去兩年經過全面測試，將會整合到維珍尼亞級潛艇的影像系統上，而預計會在今年11月開始服役的科羅拉多號（USS Colorado）將會率先採用此系統。至於現役的維珍尼亞級潛艇，亦會循正常裝備更新程序裝上Xbox控制器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/79068\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F79068&h=f1f99453&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef0da0dc5ba6ae1db150189a048e7e335743b93a","tid":405990,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/79068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F79068&d=jWODVY9xXFwp0mmthCJ0jC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bd5cf1f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/79068</a>"},{"pid":"3395df9b6080403c986f367545f420d5d8431311","tid":405990,"uid":46527,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"去換嘅話去common room或者士兵休息室拎個就得！"},{"pid":"92c0ed649729fb0056d3193eb707bf8853ba70f9","tid":405990,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"每個人有專屬手制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a9fdc90912ecfc421908c56e02713f6e392028","tid":405990,"uid":26601,"like":176,"dislike":0,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"電競選手上戰場不是夢"},{"pid":"6156ac1aed778e7260849eb50d54d5d1f92f1f2c","tid":405990,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d211a9f5c77c4eaac18980e6f9021d8ed4250e6f","tid":405990,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfirmware 俾人hack"},{"pid":"55f67a81131ba142c68739e484f3435c06e13822","tid":405990,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"xbox elite 手制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4b99343ed69542c2c8e5044d632a2393a4c830","tid":405990,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以美軍呢排成日撞船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e493e5d6a30